text: Jaba yasabata uni nirasa bha'e, taba ekantama basera sallaha garna lage tyasamadhye jo sabaima jestha thiyo tyasale bhan'yo’’ timila'i thaha chaina ki pitale timibata allahako kasama li'era punah pratijna gara'eka chan, ra tyasabhanda agadi yusuphako barema timi bhula garisakeka chau. Pheri ma tyasa rastrabata jamdina jaba sam'maki pitaji aphai mala'i ijajata nadi'una, va allaha nai mero barema phaisala garos. Tyo nai asala phaisala garnevala ho
